description:
After being a shut-in, Haruto is reincarnated as a baby. And amazingly, that baby is a prince! However, he's abandoned in a forest on the day he's born because of his low magic level... What will be the fate of Haruto, who was inadvertently given 1000 times the normal amount of magic by the goddess of reincarnation without anyone noticing?!

(Source: Crunchyroll)

tags.name: Reincarnation
tags.description: Features a character being born again after death, typically as another person or in another world.

tags.name: Magic
tags.description: Prominently features magical elements or the use of magic.

tags.name: Isekai
tags.description: Features characters being transported into an alternate world setting and having to adapt to their new surroundings.

tags.name: Kemonomimi
tags.description: Prominently features humanoid characters with animal ears.

tags.name: Rehabilitation
tags.description: Prominently features the recovery of a character who became incapable of social life or work.

tags.name: Family Life
tags.description: Centers around the activities of a family unit.

tags.name: Male Protagonist
tags.description: Main character is male.

tags.name: Hikikomori
tags.description: Prominently features a character who withdraws from social life, often seeking extreme isolation.

tags.name: Henshin
tags.description: Prominently features character or costume transformations which often grant special abilities.

tags.name: Conspiracy
tags.description: Contains one or more factions controlling or attempting to control the world from the shadows.

tags.name: Female Harem
tags.description: Main cast features the protagonist plus several female characters who are romantically interested in them.

tags.name: Demons
tags.description: Prominently features malevolent otherworldly creatures.

tags.name: Superhero
tags.description: Prominently features super-powered humans who aim to serve the greater good.

tags.name: Revenge
tags.description: Prominently features a character who aims to exact punishment in a resentful or vindictive manner.

tags.name: Time Skip
tags.description: Features a gap in time used to advance the story.

tags.name: Age Regression
tags.description: Prominently features a character who was returned to a younger state.

tags.name: Gods
tags.description: Prominently features a character of divine or religious nature.

tags.name: Yandere
tags.description: Prominently features a character who is obsessively in love with another, to the point of acting deranged or violent.

tags.name: Snowscape
tags.description: Prominently or partially set in a snowy environment.

tags.name: Skeleton
tags.description: Prominently features skeleton(s) as a character.

tags.name: Clone
tags.description: Prominently features a character who is an artificial exact copy of another organism.
